Package: VFtree
Type: Package
Title: visualization of combined Virulence Factors and Phylogenetic Tree
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Bihan Zhu
Authors@R: person("Zhu", "Bihan", email = "bihan.zhu@mail.utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Bihan Zhu <bihan.zhu@mail.utoronto.ca>
Description: VFtree is a package which is  able to  take the tree input in newick format and the vfactors present/absent data in csv/tsv file , process the data, constructed visualization of the core genome phylogenetic tree to associate virulence factor presence/absence with other strain attributes.
